headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Government Contractors Lose Ground, Tapestry Rises
summary: The S&P 500 slipped 0.6% on Thursday, Nov. 14, 2024, as hotter-than-expected wholesale inflation data clouded the outlook on interest-rate cuts.
